it could. also did you try and put some oil in #3 to see if the
compression improved. (was this with a hot engine)

> Is there an article out there for adjusting the valves on the Type 4 engine 
> especially with lifters? I still don't have a Bentley, the cheapest Bentley 
> I can find costs 70.00. I'm only familiar with Type 1 engine valve 
